{"lastModified":1772828721077,"uri":"c::10923570597::vessel::f4728230-bdff-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef","yachtType":["Sailing"],"description":"Base / Home Port:\nKomodo National Park: Labuan Bajo, NTT (Summer) & Raja Ampat National Park: Sorong, West Papua (Winter)\n\nOperating Area:\nBali, Lombok, Sumbawa, Sumba, Flores, Alor, Timor (Summer) & Ambon, Banda, Halmahera, Ternate, West Papua, Raja Ampat, Kaimana, Biak, Wakatobi (Winter).\nPlease kindly find our signature itinerary for Komodo, Banda, and Raja Ampat in the attachment section.\n\nA Wellness Retreat on the Water\nKayra, an exquisite 38-meter luxury yacht, redefines wellness and relaxation at sea. Hosting up to 8 guests in four beautifully designed cabins, Kayra combines elegance with a sense of calm. The master suite on the bridge deck offers a panoramic 270-degree view, a private sanctuary with an expansive en-suite bathroom complete with a bathtub. Just steps away, the spa room, gym, sauna, and ice bath await for rejuvenation, complemented by a sunbathing area on the captain's bridge. The VIP cabin, complete with its own balcony on the main deck, offers an intimate connection to the sea, while alfresco dining on the foredeck allows for starlit evenings or shaded, breezy afternoons. With a top deck lounge, bar, and Jacuzzi, Kayra promises an unforgettable journey of wellness, luxury, and breathtaking views.","blueprint":{"name":"KAYRA","images":["/media/media::image::c::10923570597::vessel::f4728230-bdff-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::e2cbd230-7d66-11f0-955e-952f717b2be5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10923570597::vessel::f4728230-bdff-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::e2ca99b0-7d66-11f0-955e-952f717b2be5/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10923570597::vessel::f4728230-bdff-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::3ea10630-6e98-11f0-b33d-63eef4fca675/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::10923570597::vessel::f4728230-bdff-11ef-866a-ad7f2dece8ef::assets::3ea2daf0-6e98-11f0-b33d-63eef4fca675/{imageVaria